race.comment: TIPSY TESS (8) is a talented type who boasts a strong winning strike-rate at this distance. Has been on speed to score at her last couple of runs. Latest win recorded a handy 30.51 at Angle Park. Ran the fastest time on the program in her latest win. The one to beat again. QUEST FOR ANGEL (3) made light work of the tricky draw with a fast early sectional but gathered in and had to settle for the minors, finishing second (31.39) at Angle Park over 530m. Expecting another good run. CAWBOURNE ADELE (1) took the sit on the lead from an outside box but levelled up and drew clear to score (31.03) at Angle Park in a Special conditions race over 530m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Should feature again. I'M VANILLA BABY (4) will be thereabouts after strong recent winning form.
